name: Config 2022 Pau Ferrer
description:
Hi there,

I am an ex-Commercial Manager (over 15 years) and now retrained as a Full Stack Developer and since this year UI/UX Designer.

In 2019 I discovered Software Engineering and I realised that I wanted to do that for living, so I began my self-training and this year I am looking to start my own business and help SMEs in their digital journey!!
